  "L3": "Arc City, level: Clear the Wall. Author a parabola beam. The dark node to light is at x 8, y 0.5. A wall 4 units tall stands at x 5. A gate with an opening from y 3.4 to 4.3 is at x 6.5. Aim the beam through any gates, over any walls, to reach the node.",
  "L4": "Arc City, level: Switchback. Author a V-shaped, absolute-value beam. The dark node to light is at x 5, y 1. A gate with an opening from y 4 to 6 is at x 2. A gate with an opening from y 4 to 6 is at x 8. Aim the beam through any gates, over any walls, to reach the node.",
}
`;

